elements.name: Como usuario verifico que el post esté creado y el autor tenga el nuevo nombre

steps.name: I wait for a signal containing "logged" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "creating" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "posting" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "post created" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "editing profile" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "edited profile" for 30 seconds
I select the post with title "$$name_1"
I check the post author is "$$name_2"

name: Crear un post y modificar el nombre de autor, que el usuario vea el nuevo nombre
